title: Ep. 672 - The Disguised Game - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Rana comes dressed up as a 'baba' to Gokuldham. The ladies are impressed by his words and take him to Jetha's house. Meanwhile, Rana is making plans to put Daya in danger

title: Ep. 673 - The Poisoned Sweets - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The people of Gokuldham invite trouble for themselves when they let Rana inside. He gives them sweets which are poisoned. In this meantime, they kidnap Daya.

title: Ep. 674 - Where Is Daya? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena comes home and sees everybody lying unconscious. The inspector and Tapu Sena go to Jetha's house. None of them remembers what had happened. But, soon they realize Daya is missing.

title: Ep. 675 - Daya Gets Special Treatment - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Though Daya is kidnapped, she is treated with respect by Rana and his gang. She sends a video to Jetha and others about her safety.

title: Ep. 676 - A Face - Off - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: To save Daya, the residents of Gokuldham come up with a plan. Meanwhile, Daya explains the importance of a brother and her relationship with him. She also says she could sacrifice everything for him.

title: Ep. 677 - A Lesson For The Good - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The residents of Gokuldham and Rana come face to face. Later, Daya words instill wisdom in Rana's wife and she agrees to jail her brother. Rana also agrees to get onto the right path.

title: Ep. 678 -  Janmashtami Celeberations - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham is celebrating Janmashtami in a grand way. Everything is set and the celebrations go ahead with joy and laughter.

title: Ep. 679 - A Plan To Stop Dr. Hathi - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dr. Hathi's name has come up for 'Dahi Handi'. The residents of Gokuldham are worried about his participation. They find numerous ways to deal to stop him and finally arrive with a plan.

title: Ep. 681 - Dr. Hathi Acts Stubborn - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Hathi is dressed up as 'Krishna' but when none of the residents turn up, he says he would leave the society. The celebrations are about to begin when an elephant enters Gokuldham.

title: Ep. 682 - Babita Visits Jetha's Shop - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita goes to Jetha's house for help. Meanwhile, Chachaji and Tapu enter the house. Later, Babita goes to Jetha's shop and a mishap happens.

title: Ep. 683 - Need For Improvement - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A customer comes to Sodhi's Garage in order to get his car repaired. They enter into an argument when the customer questions Sodhi's work. Later, Sodhi's wife lands herself in trouble.

title: Ep. 684 - Daya Helps Roshan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Roshan sprains her hand and is unable to cook food for the guests. She asks to help fro her friends but they are busy. Finally, Daya comes to her rescue and helps her out.

title: Ep. 685 - An Abundance Of Food - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya takes the food to Roshan's house. In the meantime, the others also come with different varieties of food. This makes everybody happy.

title: Ep. 686 - Goli's Anger - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Nattu kaka and Baga have come up with a scheme that doesn't interest Jetha. Later, the kids start playing and Goli breaks the racket in anger which comes into Bhide's notice.

title: Ep. 687 - A Meeting For Ganpati Puja Preparations - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi goes to Jetha's house to call him for the meeting. While everybody wants to leave from the meeting, Bhide's smartness stops them. Meanwhile, a stranger enters their meeting with a request for the Puja.
